OL,6,GThe BBC belongs to all of us.  A
OL,7,Gstatement of the obvious, you might
OL,8,Gthink, but in a world of division
OL,9,Gthat can be a burden and not a
OL,10,Gblessing.
OL,12,FIt is very easy for us all to escape
OL,13,Finto the echo chambers of social
OL,14,Fmedia.  No matter what your opinion
OL,15,For how niche your interests, you will
OL,16,Ffind others online who share your
OL,17,Foutlook.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age
OL,4,Cof social media
