OL,6,FIt might be a bit of harmless fun
OL,7,Flike nostalgia for old style
OL,8,FPresentation or it could be a
OL,9,Fpotentially harmful or extreme
OL,10,Fpolitical opinion.
OL,12,FMeanwhile the BBC and the other major
OL,13,Fbroadcasters are not echo chambers `
OL,14,Fthey are the public spaces we all
OL,15,Fhave stakes in and where any opinion
OL,16,Fwhich is respectfully expressed
OL,17,Fshould have a place.
OL,19,FThe row over Gary Lineker's tweet and
OL,20,Fthe BBC's response sits at the centre
OL,21,Fof this.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age
OL,4,Cof social media
