OL,6,FThere is an alarming tendency in
OL,7,Fcertain quarters to see the world in
OL,8,Fblack and white ` you are either
OL,9,Fcompletely and unquestioningly for
OL,10,Fsomething or against it.
OL,12,FThere is no need to understand where
OL,13,Fan opponent is coming from, far less
OL,14,Fa need to engage constructively with
OL,15,Ftheir arguments and accept they might
OL,16,Fhave a point. You are either for
OL,17,Fsomething or against it.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age
OL,4,Cof social media
