OL,6,FFor a lot of people, the row over
OL,7,FGary Lineker's tweet seems to be a
OL,8,Fblack and white issue.
OL,10,FTheir view of whether the BBC's
OL,11,Finitial actions were appropriate
OL,12,Fdepends entirely on whether they
OL,13,Fagreed with the sentiments in the
OL,14,Ftweet.
OL,16,FMissing from this intemperate well of
OL,17,Fsocial media poison were two
OL,18,Freasonable positions which I suspect
OL,19,Fmany people hold.
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age
OL,4,Cof social media
