OL,6,
OL,7,F I agree with Gary but BBC Sport
OL,8,Fpresenters should not comment on
OL,9,Fissues like this publicly.
OL,10,F I don't agree with Gary but he has
OL,11,Fa perfect right to voice his views.
OL,13,FIf only a few more people realised
OL,14,Fthere were shades of grey.
OL,16,FAdd to the toxic mix, the current BBC
OL,17,Fchairman and the fact the director-
OL,18,Fgeneral was active in local
OL,19,FConservative politics 30 years ago
OL,20,Fand you can see the perfect recipe
OL,21,Ffor conspiracy theorists.
