OL,6,FIn the meantime, the review of the
OL,7,FBBC's social media guidelines will
OL,8,Fget underway in earnest.
OL,10,FHopefully any reasonable person will
OL,11,Fbe able to distinguish between those
OL,12,Fwho appear on BBC programmes and
OL,13,Fthose who might be seen as
OL,14,Frepresenting the BBC itself.
OL,16,FI say hopefully because there are
OL,17,Fundoubtedly grey areas. Not least the
OL,18,Fquestion of those freelance
OL,19,Fpresenters who are principally
OL,20,Fassociated with key BBC output.
