OL,6,FBut there is nothing new. Thirty five
OL,7,Fyears ago, David Icke somehow managed
OL,8,Fto combine being a BBC Sport
OL,9,Fpresenter with being a Green Party
OL,10,Fspokesman. (This was before his
OL,11,Fnotorious appearance on Wogan and all
OL,12,Fwhich followed.)
OL,14,FAnd can you imagine having a regular
OL,15,Fcontributor to children's programmes
OL,16,Fwith right wing views which went well
OL,17,Fbeyond mainstream Conservative
OL,18,Fpolitics? Well did anyone suggest
OL,19,FNorris McWhirter should have been
OL,20,Ftaken off Record Breakers in the 70s
OL,21,Fand early 80s?
OL,3,CImpartiality and the BBC in the age
OL,4,Cof social media
